<paragraph id="BE3835517222F7E8B1992A115159DA81" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="936C1147B58F899F7178E05069B67990" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
<taxonomicName id="23F8C90CFF0D5F20CF8CE0CBF4F7E9E8" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
was traditionally considered as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="246894EADF756D26C501EEC20CC6E4F1" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum nobile" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nobile">Hedychrum nobile</taxonomicName>
(Scopoli). No specimen labelled as 
<taxonomicName id="55E29868AB50A66B6CE9F24DBC0A173D" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
was found in 
<normalizedToken id="9AA70638FF156E9561DD4F93EF528C7F" originalValue="Lepeletier’s">Lepeletier's</normalizedToken>
collection at MNHN (
<bibRefCitation id="D6600862BF539156384CBA4AB485A234" author="Buysson, R du" journalOrPublisher="Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" pagination="518 - 580" title="Etude des Chrysidides du Museum de Paris." volume="66" year="1898">du Buysson 1898</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="1AF273E2DBCBA186E7C0E1A83EDBC695" author="Buysson, R du" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin du Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" pagination="159 - 169" title="Catalogue des Insectes Hymenopteres de la famille des Chrysidides du Museum de Paris." volume="5" year="1899">1899</bibRefCitation>
). Therefore, there is the possibility that the specimens in the Spinola collection are syntypes; the male in this collection belongs to the species 
<taxonomicName id="809A13E128A1D025ABB32460619E646B" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum gerstaeckeri" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gerstaeckeri">Hedychrum gerstaeckeri</taxonomicName>
Chevrier, 1869, whereas the female belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="96B446151E0FB44F295B234E385BE8A6" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum rutilans" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutilans">Hedychrum rutilans</taxonomicName>
Dahlbom, 1854. 
<bibRefCitation id="069F017B2FA968ADC5130812C4DECC6F" author="Buysson, R du" editor="Andre, E" journalOrPublisher="Dubosclard, Paris" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" pagination="13 - 758" title="Species des Hymenopteres d'Europe &amp; d'Algerie" year="1891 - 1896">du Buysson (1895</bibRefCitation>
: 18) in his &quot;Catalogue 
<normalizedToken id="80B67C1A761F7E40DDB4739A2D60486A" originalValue="méthodique">methodique</normalizedToken>
des Chrysidides de France&quot; listed 
<taxonomicName id="3955D187368406B9498DB2ACD085441F" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="9D0095C9F6B1A52B0614E1B708A33B2B" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum rutilans" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutilans">Hedychrum rutilans</taxonomicName>
, without having considered the priority of the name 
<taxonomicName id="76E26212562075AC6994E68C99DFE925" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
over 
<taxonomicName id="79C1CF395A90044CAF5BB0D04B411C43" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum rutilans" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutilans">Hedychrum rutilans</taxonomicName>
. The short description of 
<taxonomicName id="F77CE009FB76DA943E01FB6DE391CD23" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
does not allow identification of this species and part of the description is doubtful (&quot;
<normalizedToken id="C797F49DF6D5ED4EC5AE3FED1583FA8B" originalValue="Tête">Tete</normalizedToken>
et corcelet verts&quot;) because the colour of head and pronotum and mesonotum in 
<taxonomicName id="D19B754E41E470FB3C88CADEE8A8C05F" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum nobile" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nobile">Hedychrum nobile</taxonomicName>
has no contrasts. Confidence in that Lepeletier described at least one specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="1D7E31974138574E39921DAAFE18C990" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum rutilans" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutilans">Hedychrum rutilans</taxonomicName>
comes from the colour drawing (
<bibRefCitation id="63118BAA3FAE430DABAC6E1C1A213ECD" author="Lepeletier, ALM" journalOrPublisher="Annales du Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle" pageId="74" pageNumber="75" pagination="115 - 129" title="Memoire sur quelques especes nouvelles d'insectes de la section des Hymenopteres appeles les Portetuyaux, et sur les caracteres de cette famille et des genres qui la composent." volume="7" year="1806">Lepeletier 1806</bibRefCitation>
: pl. 6: fig. 8). In this drawing, it is clear that pronotum and mesonotum are green, contrasting with the rest of the mesosoma, which is blue. Therefore, based on the drawing and the diagnosis given by 
<bibRefCitation id="FFF1250DF6BFAD56E04875536B31CA9C" author="Buysson, R du" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin du Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" pagination="159 - 169" title="Catalogue des Insectes Hymenopteres de la famille des Chrysidides du Museum de Paris." volume="5" year="1899">du Buysson (1899)</bibRefCitation>
, we can assume the synonym 
<taxonomicName id="070ADA74C6CC6231FE5E97E9DC7BE716" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum rutilans" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutilans">Hedychrum rutilans</taxonomicName>
Dahlbom, 1854 = 
<taxonomicName id="B95B3D48FB4806E4917E04D2541691D5" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
Lepeletier, 1806.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DA766329873BC863544701684AFD8C3F" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
<taxonomicName id="DD3F1AFBF99AA38D78C97A10D24E4A95" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
was misinterpreted by 
<bibRefCitation id="7C2E8DC639695DF0D160DE1F49724D99" author="Dahlbom, AG" journalOrPublisher="Nicolai, Berlin" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" title="Hymenoptera Europaea praecipue Borealia, formis typicis nonnullis, specierum generumve exoticorum propter nexum systematicum associatis, per familias, genera, species et varietates disposita atque descripta ab Adrea Gustavo Dahlbom. Chrysis in sensu Linneano" year="1854">Dahlbom (1854</bibRefCitation>
: 79), who placed it in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="D43AADE463C57145EA7FB1E4ACD2C4FF" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum lucidulum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidulum">Hedychrum lucidulum</taxonomicName>
(Fabricius, 1775) [currently 
<taxonomicName id="7E90C3027F1806753EB952AACC21E1EC" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum nobile" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nobile">Hedychrum nobile</taxonomicName>
(Scopoli, 1763)] without having examined the type. He simply listed &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="227029DBF957B65B5F19904C5B660835" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
Dufour in litt.&quot;. Based on this work, all the other authors, from 
<bibRefCitation id="8500AE01422C7102A660787705177826" author="Dalla Torre, CG" journalOrPublisher="Engelmann, Lipsiae" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" title="Catalogus Hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus. Chrysididae (Tubulifera). Tip. G." year="1892">Dalla Torre (1892</bibRefCitation>
: 34) to 
<bibRefCitation id="30E8B6981BBC7E028E5AE313778E5896" author="Kimsey, LS" journalOrPublisher="University Press, New York" pageId="73" pageNumber="74" title="The Chrysidid Wasps of the World." year="1991">Kimsey and Bohart (1991</bibRefCitation>
: 217) placed 
<taxonomicName id="E6F24BCCAD8FBDD6CEEE646492A78BE8" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="97B89BF6E87575572E9B4E8059A01ED4" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum nobile" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nobile">Hedychrum nobile</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9143015AD871C88B808104630A1AA25F" lastPageId="62" lastPageNumber="63" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
Since the name 
<taxonomicName id="DCDD9C95205CC5A8810620E3EA17DA41" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum rutilans" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutilans">
<pageBreakToken id="247A9787C4D5AD0BA8A5F10B10EAD615" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" start="start">Hedychrum</pageBreakToken>
rutilans
</taxonomicName>
is currently in prevailing usage, we propose the reversal of precedence in accordance with the Art. 23.9 of the Code. In fact, the prevailing usage must be maintained when the two conditions are both met: the senior synonym has not been used as a valid name after 1899 and the junior synonym has been used for this species as a valid name in at least 25 works published by at least 10 authors in the immediately preceding 50 years and encompassing a span of not less than 10 years. The name 
<taxonomicName id="C6495FFC84795A83D663495B33BB5ED3" authority="Latreille, 1806" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" class="Insecta" family="Chrysididae" genus="Hedychrum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hedychrum alterum" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alterum">Hedychrum alterum</taxonomicName>
